<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-12">
    <h1 class="page-header">
      MAZI Zone <small>GuestBook Admin</small>
    </h1>
  </div>
</div>
<% unless error_msg.nil? %>
  <div class="alert alert-danger">
    <p><%= error_msg %></p>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="row">
  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-12'>
    <p>
      You can use the tools bellow to perform various administrative actions for the MAZI GuestBook application.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Moderate Posted Content
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to moderate the posted content."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>Use the button bellow to go to the appropriate page in order to moderate the posted content of the GuestBook application (default username: admin, default password: mazizone).</p>
            <a class="btn btn-success pull-right" title="Moderate posted content" href="http://local.mazizone.eu:8081/#admin" target="_blank">Go</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Welcome Message
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to change the maximum file size."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>You can use the form bellow to change the welcome message in the GuestBook application. </br>The current welcome message is: <b> <%= welcomeMessage %></b></p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/welcome_message" method="post">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" name="welcome_message" value="<%= welcomeMessage %>" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 8px">
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Save" title="Save welcome message"/>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Background Image
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to upload a new background image."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>Current image: <%= cur_background_img %> </br>You can use the form bellow to upload a new background image for the GuestBook application.</p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/background_image" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="file" name="guestbook_background_image" class="form-control filestyle" data-buttonText="Browse">
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary pull-right" value="Upload" title="Upload background image"/>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Maximum File Size for uploads
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to change the maximum file size."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>You can use the form bellow to change the maximum file size for uploads in the GuestBook application. </br>The current maximum file size is: <b> <%= maximumFileSize %> MBytes</b></p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/maxfilesize" method="post">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" name="maxfilesize" value="<%= maximumFileSize %>" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 8px">
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Save" title="Save max file size" style="margin-bottom: 7px"/>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Tags
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to add/remove tags."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>You can use the input field bellow to add/remove tags. Then use the button bellow to save the tags for the GuestBook application.</p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/tags" method="post">
              <input name="tags" id="singleFieldTags2" value="<%= tags %>">
              <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Save" title="Save tags"/>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Auto Expand Comment
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to change the auto expand comment feature."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>You can use the button bellow to change the auto expand comment feature. The current value is: <b><%= auto_expand_comment %></b></p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/auto_expand_comment" method="post">
              <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Change"/>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='col-md-12 col-lg-6'>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading">
        <div class="panel-title">Submision Name Requirement
          <i class="fa fa-info-circle pull-right" aria-hidden="true" title="You can use this to change the wether the name is required or not."></i>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- panel body -->
      <div class="panel-body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <p>You can use the button bellow to change the requirement of the name for a new post. The current value is: <b><%= submision_name_req %></b></p>
            <form action="/application_admin/guestbook/submission_name_req" method="post">
              <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Change"/>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
